## Static Assets ŌĆö Font Awesome (Self-Hosted)
Font Awesome is served locally from `ui/static/vendor/fontawesome/` ŌĆö **not** from a CDN.

```
ui/static/vendor/fontawesome/
  css/all.min.css      ŌåÉ referenced as /static/vendor/fontawesome/css/all.min.css
  webfonts/            ŌåÉ fa-solid-900.woff2, fa-brands-400.woff2, etc.
```

`base.html` loads it with a plain `<link>` (not `asset_url()` ŌĆö it doesn't go through the esbuild manifest). All child templates that previously loaded FA from cdnjs now use the same local path.

**Never re-add the cdnjs CDN link** ŌĆö it is blocked in the local dev environment.
